snippet.title: Yanvania 2022
snippet.description:
This is a game project that I developed in November 2022.

Every October, I try to release a short horror-themed game project on Halloween. It's kinda like a personal "Game Jam."

For 2022, I decided to re-imagine the "Yanvania" minigame that I released in 2015. It was fun to revisit this old idea 7 years later, and try to improve the production value as much as possible.

If you're interested in playing the game yourself, you can download it here: 

https://www.mediafire.com/file/leas2xluem288rb/Yanvania+2022.zip/file
